{"tid":1830852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方稱劉頴匡從沒終止集會　促便衣警展委任證是刁難　","createTime":"2020-01-20T02:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:10:30.000Z","uid":48093,"like":50,"dislike":271,"uniUserReply":144,"replies":[{"pid":"6238f282d249f7825763197523b3958b2c756741","tid":1830852,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"警方港島總區高級警司吳樂俊說，「民間集會團隊」發言人劉頴匡昨日由始至終，沒有宣布腰斬集會。吳樂俊說，當時附近有人堵路和破壞閉路電視，主辦單位有派糾察維持秩序，但認為他們控制不到現場情況，所以警方要求終止集會，但劉頴匡態度不合作。<br />\n<br />\n吳樂俊接受本台節目《千禧年代》電話訪問時說，劉頴匡當時要求警民關係科的便衣警員出示委任證，認為是刁難警方，煽動群眾情緒，不過最後其中一名警員有展示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n記者翻看片段，見到劉頴匡昨日下午4時許，透過揚聲器宣布終止集會，並呼籲在場人士向金鐘方向和平散去，大會亦有用揚聲器叫糾察協助市民離開，並呼籲大家冷靜，不要「搞」 便衣警員。"},{"pid":"98c58abebab30202fa86a448c51ed136b3d7f8e7","tid":1830852,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9a423de735e9a490329d0d3ec880a5b070dde9","tid":1830852,"uid":60924,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪講左中止"},{"pid":"fe0ff046b25c0fab2c236230b7c994d6634048ca","tid":1830852,"uid":13914,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"Goodest logic, 唔show證點知係咪便衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9798051baefde08b333c00b474b92985c85b933","tid":1830852,"uid":291750,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"發神經"},{"pid":"1d81a000a9a28352910ae223139fe1255b68a2be","tid":1830852,"uid":973,"like":35,"dislik